WEBVTT

00:02.102 --> 00:04.503
        Cheers <i>is filmed</i>        
 <i>before a live studio audience.</i> 

00:04.571 --> 00:06.205
This is sick.                   

00:06.272 --> 00:07.873
Just stop harassing me.         

00:07.941 --> 00:09.842
You'll get your money           
when I'm good and ready.        

00:09.943 --> 00:11.076
And if you try                  
to contact me                   

00:11.144 --> 00:12.745
at the workplace                
one more time,                  

00:12.812 --> 00:14.480
I'm gonna turn you over         
to the authorities!             

00:14.547 --> 00:16.982
             Jerk.              

00:17.050 --> 00:19.184
            Which one of your   
                  kids was that?

00:19.285 --> 00:20.919
  That was not one of my kids.  

00:20.987 --> 00:22.855
    I don't talk to my kids     
        that way.               

00:22.922 --> 00:24.623
Bill collector, then, huh?      
No,                             

00:24.691 --> 00:25.991
    it was my mother.           

00:26.126 --> 00:27.960
Her Social Security check       

00:28.028 --> 00:31.830
  is late, like it's my fault   
    she's getting old.          

00:35.335 --> 00:37.336
Did you hear the way            
she talked to her mother?       

00:37.404 --> 00:39.905
I could never talk              
to my mother like that.         

00:39.973 --> 00:43.042
          Hey, Carla,           
 could you give my mom a call?  

00:43.143 --> 00:45.177
      (theme song begins)       

